         <div type="translation" resp="#jmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p><supplied reason="lost">When emperor Caesar Publius Licinius</supplied> Egnatius Gallienus Pius, Felix Augustus, <supplied reason="lost">greatest</supplied> victor in Germany, greatest victor in <supplied reason="lost">Dacia</supplied>, greatest victor in Persia, <supplied reason="lost">chief priest</supplied>, held tribunician power for the twelfth time, acclaimed victor, consul five times, father of the country, proconsul, and to <supplied reason="lost">Salonina</supplied>, wife of Gal<supplied reason="omitted">li</supplied>enus. Milestone nineteen.</p></div>
